{"tid":517573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【涉向非禮案疑犯勒索掩口費　休班警長4月區院受審】","createTime":"2018-01-02T12:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T15:03:07.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65ebf05df8717726821644fc5b3ad1f28cd0d369","tid":517573,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"一名休班警長，去年7月在港鐵太子站截查一名涉嫌非禮女乘客的疑犯，之後將對方帶返旺角警署途中時，涉嫌向男子勒索一萬港元「掩口費」，並涉向對方盜取一萬港元，早前被警方拘捕，及後被控勒索及盜竊兩罪，案件今日（1月2日）在區域法院提訊。<br />\n<br />\n49歲的被告張偉基不認罪，案件將排期到4月9日開審，預計需審訊3日。<br />\n<br />\n被告張偉基本來已經退休，但之後以合約方式重返警隊，現時現場被停職。"},{"pid":"e695d5610421894bf90e425b1197b81253628506","tid":517573,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鳩犬搵日唔上報可以嗎？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485f4c44c0c5d788c0d9dfec256d1bdb05293aab","tid":517573,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">NTW，又一隻呢D圍威畏厄退休金再翻閹文盲廢老犬？？？</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"012cf090cd5f1135cea8edce4b089df1ce6bd67b","tid":517573,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11407c9ab1afd52ce591a6f28f3b1796dce35025","tid":517573,"uid":88029,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8365235fb5b499276113ec8303ec4b77dd3e78a2","tid":517573,"uid":39698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"大家快D睇定五億探長雷洛傳學定野"},{"pid":"4f15afe1c3885f8c1d3c98061a1b95a39e72994f","tid":51757